perl5.branches      5.26
perl5.setup         Log-Dispatchouli 2.016

platforms           darwin
maintainers         nomaintainer
license             {Artistic-1 GPL}

#supported_archs     noarch

description         Log::Dispatchouli - a simple wrapper around Log::Dispatch

long_description    Log::Dispatchouli is a thin layer above Log::Dispatch \
                    and meant to make it dead simple to add logging to a \
                    program without having to think much about categories, \
                    facilities, levels, or things like that.

